text.section:
Except as provided in subsection (g) of this section, this section applies to:
Every motor vehicle carrying a passenger for hire;
Every school vehicle carrying any passenger;
Every bus that is owned or operated by a church and carrying any passenger;
Every vehicle carrying as cargo a flammable liquid or an explosive; and
Every vehicle carrying hazardous materials of a type and quantity requiring placarding under federal hazardous materials regulations.
